Adia Services Inc said itagreed to sell 500,000 shares of common stock to its principalstockholder, Adia S.A., at a price based on the current marketprice.    The sale will raise Adia S.A.'s ownership in the company to74.7 pct from 72.7 pct, Adia said.    The company also said it intends to use proceeds from thestock sale to retire debt, for working capital and for generalcorporate purposes. Reuter&#3;